channel.title: “Goodbye my father” by YANEECK
channel.description:
Hi,
I’ve made a classical song and it’s the first time ever for me to create this kind of music. It’s sad and beautiful at the same time. You are welcome to share your thoughts on the song.
https://soundcloud.com/yaneeck/goodbye-my-father
Take care, Tomasz
